quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  43,1,“. Hâ-Mîm
  43,2,“Ndikulumbilira buku lofotokoza momveka
  43,3,“Ndithu Ife talichita bukuli (Qur’an) kukhala chowerengedwa m’Chiarabu kuti muzindikire
  43,4,"“Ndipo ndithu bukuli (Qur’an) lili m’manthu wa mabuku onse (Lawhi Mahfudh) limene lili kwa Ife; (ndipo ndi buku) lotukuka, la mawu anzeru"
  43,5,“Kodi tisiye kukukumbutsani chifukwa chakuti ndinu anthu opyola malire (pochita zoipa)
  43,6,“Ndipo tidatumiza aneneri ambiri kwa anthu akale
  43,7,“Ndipo palibe mneneri aliyense amene amawadzera koma amam’chitira chipongwe
  43,8,“Choncho tidawaononga amene adali amphamvu kuposa iwo (Aquraish) ndipo ladutsa fanizo la (zilango zomwe zidawapeza) anthu akale
  43,9,"“Ndipo ukawafunsa: “Ndani adalenga thambo ndi nthaka?” Ndithu ayankha kuti: “Adazilenga (Allah) Mwini Mphamvu, Wodziwa.”"
  43,10,“Amene wakupangirani nthaka kukhala choyala ndipo adakupangirani njira mmenemo kuti muongoke (ndikukafika kumene mukufuna)
  43,11,“Ndiponso amene watsitsa madzi kuchokera kumwamba mwamuyeso; chifukwa cha madziwo tidaukitsa mudzi wakufa. Momwemonso inu mudzatulutsidwa (mmanda)
  43,12,“Ndiponso amene walenga zinthu zonse ziwiriziwiri (chachimuna ndi chachikazi). Ndipo adakupangirani zombo ndi ziweto zimene mukukwera
  43,13,"“Kuti mukhazikike mwaubwino pamisana paizo, kenako mukumbukire mtendere wa Mbuye wanu mukakhazikika pamenepo, ndipo munene: “Walemekezeka Amene watifewetsera ichi; ndipo sitikadatha kuchifewetsa ndi kuchigwiritsa ntchito.”"
  43,14,““Ndipo ndithu ife kwa Mbuye wathu ndiko kobwerera.”
  43,15,"“Ndipo amuikira gawo mwa akapolo Ake. (Kuti ndi ana a Allah.) Ndithu munthu, ngwamsulizo woonekera poyera"